title: Sam Hill # 1-7 (Archie Comics)
description:
Six issues published by Archi Comics 1950-1952

Issue six is missing unfortunately, but hopefully someone else out there will be able to upload it and fill out the gap

The Harry Lucey might not ring as many bells as, say, Alex Thoth, Milton Canif or Roy Crane, but in this series he showed a flair for visual narrative and composition that isn't unlike what the others mentioned usually is associated with

A pretty sweet detective series
